column5: Greetings, I have "met" many wonderful folks over the last few years through this Canada Forum on Walleye Central. I extend to all of you and your families a heartfelt Merry Christmas and Happy/Healthy New Year! Good fishing and tight lines in 2019!!
Couldn't have said it better myself, Merry Christmas and a Happy New Year to you and your family too!!! May the Walleye God's shine on us all for 2019!
And a Happy New Year! May you all have some great days on and off the water!
Merry Christmas and Happy New Year!!!!!

What I can say is that I visit this cyber-cabin almost every single day...all year round. I believe many of you do as well. Some of you leave an obvious trail. Others leave no trace at all. But here we all are. I wish peace, respect and kindness to everyone.
